PASSED: FY26 National Defense Authorization Act  🇺🇸

Honored to preside over the House Floor during part of the NDAA debate yesterday.

@HouseGOP secured President Trump’s peace through strength agenda by investing in our national security and ensuring our warfighters have the best Made-In-America resources.

The One Big Beautiful Bill is for ALL Texans. 

It successfully puts American families &amp; workers first, and lets Texans keep more of their money in their pockets. 

@HouseGOP and @POTUS are committed to restoring economic prosperity. https://t.co/QreifdT7qh

We must pass the One Big Beautiful Bill.

Small Businesses in East Texas will be hit with a 43.4% tax rate if the 199A Small Business Deduction expires.

@HouseGOP will ensure this doesn’t happen. https://t.co/C2FxQUm04u

🇺🇸 Tomorrow, the @WaysandMeansGOP begins marking up key pieces of the “ONE, BIG, BEAUTIFUL BILL” — legislation to slash taxes, and bring jobs back to America.

@POTUS is right: Republicans must UNITE behind @RepJasonSmith and get this done.

I look forward to tomorrow’s markup, where I’ll be fighting to advance the pro-family, pro–small business, and pro–American manufacturing values of East Texas.

The ICC’s attempts to undermine the sovereignty of Israel and the United States cannot go unchecked.

@chiproytx’s International Court Counteraction Act has PASSED the House, ensuring our nation and our greatest ally, Israel, are protected from politically motivated attacks and unjust international overreach.

We must defend the right of sovereign nations to protect themselves. 🇺🇸🇮🇱

PASSED: The Jenna Quinn Law is headed to the President's desk!

@JohnCornyn and I introduced this bicameral, commonsense bill to give students, teachers, and caregivers more tools to protect vulnerable children from child sexual abuse.

Each life is precious, and each life deserves protection at every stage. I urge @POTUS to swiftly sign this critical piece of legislation into law.
